name: BEIGE
description:
The Lifter Hamper™ was designed to help individuals with bad backs, those who are pregnant, the elderly or for anyone looking for a more convenient way to do laundry. 

Laundry with ease
As you put your laundry in the Lifter Hamper™ the weight of the laundry causes the bag to drop until the bag is full. As you pull your laundry from the Lifter Hamper™, the laundry rises from the bottom so you do not have to reach to the bottom of the Lifter Hamper™. You no longer have to bend over to do your laundry! This is truly a one of a kind hamper.

The Lifter Hamper™ is stylish and comes in an assortment of colors.  Once you have tried the Lifter Hamper™, you will never want to go back to your old laundry hamper.
